A front-end project for the LUT Software Development Skills: Front-End 2025–26 course.
The site is about Kurkkumopo — Finland's legendary cucumber-shaped push scooter made by Plasto from 1971 to 1988. It was voted Finland's funniest toy in 2012, went viral in 2024, and came back into production in 2025.

